snippet.title: Final Factory Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Official launch trailer for Final Factory - Coming April 9, 2024 to Steam!

WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1383150/Final_Factory/?utm_source=update16

DISCORD: https://discord.gg/finalfactory

Final Factory blends factory building with a rich universe to explore. Build a vast network of automated space stations, design custom space craft, and command a massive fleet against hostile local aliens. Discover new technologies and unlock the secrets of an ancient civilization as you explore an infinite cosmos.

Original game soundtrack by Zayn Mufti https://www.zaynmuftimusic.com/
